title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 §§ 1229-1.1 - Introduction
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 §§ 1229-1.1 - Introduction

State Regulations

The provisions set forth in this Part 1229 are part of
the Uniform Fire Prevention and Building Code (the "Uniform Code") and are in
addition to, and not in limitation of, the provisions set forth in Parts 1219
through 1228 of this Title. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19
§§
1229-1.1

Adopted

New

York State Register July 6, 2022/Volume XLIV, Issue 27, eff. 7/6/2022

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
